data.description: Prepare to be amazed as you step into this beautiful home in Panhandle Valley Estates. From the moment you enter and experience the soaring entrance foyer, you'll be welcomed by a grand and elegant atmosphere. The architectural details are simply breathtaking, featuring coffered ceilings, arched passageways, and iron rail spindles that add a touch of sophistication. Hardwood floors grace the main level, leading you into an expansive gourmet kitchen adorned with exquisite granite countertops. The open floor plan allows for seamless entertaining, making it an ideal space for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories with family and friends. The owner's suite is a true oasis, offering a serene and tranquil space to unwind and rejuvenate. With its generous size, it provides ample room for relaxation and personalization. Also on the second level, you'll find three additional bedrooms, each uniquely designed to provide comfort and privacy. Two of these bedrooms share a Jack n Jill bath, adding convenience and practicality to the layout. The unfinished basement offers endless possibilities, waiting for your creative touch to turn it into the perfect space for your needs and desires. Escape to your private wooded backyard and enjoy the tranquility of nature from your deck or the charming gazebo. It's the perfect spot for enjoying your morning coffee or hosting outdoor gatherings. Panhandle Valley Estates is not only a serene retreat, but it also offers convenient access to a plethora of amenities. Enjoy proximity to shopping, restaurants, and entertainment, all just a stone's throw away. Additionally, outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the nearby JW SMITH RESERVOIR for fishing and leisurely walks. With easy access to major highways such as I-75, 675, and HWY 138, commuting to neighboring cities like Lovejoy and Fayetteville is a breeze. This home is a true masterpiece, combining elegance, functionality, and prime location. Don't miss the chance to make it your own and experience the lifestyle you've always dreamed of.
